---
<BaseLayout {...meta}>
  <section class="hero-pattern px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center"><div><p class="font-bold text-brand">Kerusi Urut</p><h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Bespoke 2 CUCKOO</h1><p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-muted">Semak maklumat Bespoke 2, harga cash atau rental bulanan, promo terkini dan kesesuaian produk untuk rumah anda.</p><div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row"><a href="https://wasap.my/60139916967" class="rounded-full bg-brand px-7 py-4 text-center font-bold text-white shadow-glow transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-dark">WhatsApp Ejen</a><a href="/products/massage-chair/" class="rounded-full border border-brand/20 bg-white px-7 py-4 text-center font-bold text-brand transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:bg-brand-soft">Produk lain</a></div></div><div class="rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-5 shadow-soft"><div class="flex aspect-[4/3] items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-[1.5rem] bg-brand-soft"><img src="/assets/images/products/massage-chair/bespoke-2/cuckoo%20bespoke%202%20massage%20chair%20kerusi%20urut%201.webp" alt="Bespoke 2" loading="lazy" class="h-full w-full object-contain p-6" /></div></div></div></section><section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl space-y-10"><article class="content"><h2>Kenapa pilih Bespoke 2?</h2><p>Bahagian ini ialah rangka awal untuk page produk Bespoke 2. Nanti boleh dimasukkan features, harga, plan bulanan, FAQ, gambar produk sebenar dan bukti pemasangan.</p><h2>Sesuai untuk siapa?</h2><ul><li>Customer yang mahu tahu harga sebelum order.</li><li>Customer yang mahu bandingkan model dalam kategori Kerusi Urut.</li><li>Customer yang mahu bertanya dahulu sebelum buat keputusan.</li></ul></article></div></section><div data-promo></div><div data-product-selector data-initial="massage-chair"></div><div data-agent-block></div>
</BaseLayout>
